  "body": "This is a mental not so we don't forget to investigate this. While state syncing, sometimes we seem to be importing `0` trie nodes over and over again. My hunch is that this is due to some remote peer not having the data we need. This is bad, because it slows down our progress by a significant margin and network overhead. We should add some baseline fault tracking for states too and disconnect nodes that cannot provide the necessary data.",
